{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So he too was in a bit of hot water, but it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "For two months, my pain was alleviated because the only thing that can alleviate-- not forget-- is love.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The only thing that can alleviate pain, mute pain, is love.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And two months thereafter, however, his-- his captain or-- or superior, his [RUSSIAN], said, I cannot-- I cannot cover up for you anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And this, his superior, a-- a [RUSSIAN] by the name of [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Stern ?] was a Communist and a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I remember he showed me the-- the-- red-- that's the only authentic Communist card I saw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[RUSSIAN] [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Stern ?] showed it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he would come even so, with all his Communist-- he was part of the 1918 whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He-- he was one of the Communists, of the old-time Communists.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He would still come to my sister-in-law's house and bring, I don't know, chocolates or something and say to us, talk to me in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You know, this was this great Communist who said, talk to me in Yiddish because there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But after a while, clearly, there were higher-ups than he.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He told Leonid, I cannot cover up for you anymore, and-- and you have to stop seeing her, which he refused, whereupon he was sent in to a-- to the Donbass, which was sort of a punitive colony in the Ukraine, where they placed, you know, the not very reliable elements.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was not the Gulag, by no means, because he was still in the Russian army, Leonid, but it was very rough.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And it was a very sad parting, a very sad parting, but we parted.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
